===================================================================
                          DATABASES
===================================================================
      
	Users
		id [int]				-> PK
		name [varchar]
		age [int]
		gender [varchar]
		city [varchar]
		phone [long]
		email [varchar]			-> unique
		password [varchar]
	
	Accounts
		account_number [long]	-> PK 
		balance [double]
		security_pin [int]
		user_id [int] 			-> FK (Users Table : id) 
		lock [boolean]
             
             
             

             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             